Class Patient

java.lang.Object
w23assignment1.Patient
public class Patient extends Object
File name: Patient.java Student Name: Wai Wai Chan Lab Professor: David Houtman Due Date: 26 Feb 2023 Modified: 25 Feb 2023 Description: 23W CST8284 Assignment 1 This class maintains important health information about a patient, calculates BMI value, maximum heart rate and target heart rate range for a patient, and then show all health information in a summary report.
